## TSX Twoslash Examples

With Twoslash:

```tsx twoslash
export const MyTitle = () => <h1>Title</h1>
```

Without Twoslash:

```tsx
export const MyTitle = () => <h1>Title</h1>
```

## JSX Twoslash Examples

With Twoslash:

```jsx twoslash
export const MyTitle = () => <h1>Title</h1>
```

Without Twoslash:

```jsx
export const MyTitle = () => <h1>Title</h1>
```
